    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-805c-9741-eeda7c245d6f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors test the effectiveness of their approach in Movielens and Bookcrossing with simulated sparsity and cold-start scenarios. Results show model outperforms other hybrid recommenders on these datasets.",
